<figureCitation id="632F7C3193FF0DE5BAFBC0B3D1F59DBC" captionStart="Figure 36" captionStartId="F36" captionText="Figure 36. Diagnostic characters of Pyrrhalta wulaiensis sp. nov. A antenna, male B antenna, female C aedeagus, dorsal view D ditto, lateral view E abdominal ventrite VIII F spermatheca G abdominal ventrite V, female H abdominal ventrite V, male I gonocoxae." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1039.64740.figure36" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/545566" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">36I</figureCitation>
